OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy with a scattering
OL,6,Fof showers throughout the day.
OL,7,FOccasional bright or sunny breaks
OL,8,Fdeveloping through the day with light
OL,9,Fwinds. Places in the east staying
OL,10,Fmostly dry throughout. Temperatures
OL,11,Faround average for May.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMost shower easing overnight,
OL,14,Fbut some returning in the west before
OL,15,Fdawn. Clear spells towards the east
OL,16,Fwith a patchy grass frost in rural
OL,17,Fspots.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
