OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FShowers in the west but most
OL,6,Fplaces starting dry. Heavier showers
OL,7,Fdeveloping into the afternoon which
OL,8,Fcan be slow moving in places. Warmer
OL,9,Fthan recent days.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,12,Fmixed weekend with showers in places,
OL,13,Fbut bright or sunny spells not far
OL,14,Faway. Staying mostly dry into the new
OL,15,Fweek but temperatures will start to
OL,16,Fdrop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
